      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my trusty ride and it\u2019s been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me\u2014definitely a car you can count on. It\u2019s perfect for someone looking for a dependable daily driver that still looks great on the road. I've taken good care of it, and I'm sure you'll love it as much as I have! Feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin!",
