    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound example of BMW\u2019s high-revving masterpiece. Powered by the S54 3.2L inline-six, it features individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system that has been recently overhauled for precision timing. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission offers tactile engagement, paired with a factory limited-slip differential for optimal power delivery. Crucially, the rear subframe has been reinforced, and the rod bearings have been addressed\u2014eliminating the two primary failure points of this chassis. While the exterior shows minor road wear consistent with a well-loved driver\u2019s car, the suspension geometry remains sharp with upgraded polyurethane bushings. A turn-key performance machine for the purist who values visceral feedback over a concours finish.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
