    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2017 BMW M3 finished in iconic Yas Marina Blue. This vehicle has been a dedicated daily driver for an enthusiast, offering a perfect blend of raw performance and practical luxury. The exterior paint retains a brilliant shine, though close inspection will reveal a few minor stone chips on the front bumper and a small scuff on the rear passenger-side alloy wheel\u2014typical for a car that has actually been enjoyed on the road. Inside, the Silverstone leather interior is in great shape; the seats are firm and the cabin remains smoke-free, showing only light cosmetic creasing on the driver-side bolster. Mechanically, this M3 is stout. It features a full service history with recent brake pad replacements and a fresh synthetic oil change. The twin-turbo engine delivers power smoothly across the rev range, and the dual-clutch transmission shifts with precision. All features, including the carbon fiber roof, head-up display, and heated seats, are fully operational. This is a solid, honest example of a modern legend, ready for its next chapter.",
      "price": 34500.0,
